text:
I had a very pleasant stay at HÃ´tel de la Mare. My room was a single room with private bathroom.
- location: it is in Belleville / Menilmontant area. It was very easy to reach from CDG airport. There are some metro stations close (the closest is around 10 minutes walking - Couronnes metro (line M2). There are shops, bars, restaurants and supermarkets nearby. In this area you will find people from various nationalities and religions, You will find diversity;
- room: for a single room, it has lots of space. The bathroom was also very spacious. Both were clean. There is a small kitchen with fridge, microwave and some utensils (cups, glasses, silverwares and dishes). In the cabinet there is an oven if you want to cook something. The room also has a table, AC and full body mirror;
- bed: clean and comfortable. I could sleep all night very well;
- staff: very helpful and nice;
- check-in and check-out: super easy and fast.
I have no complain about this hotel, only positive things to say.
I recommend this place 500%!!!
